Method behavioural requirements:
- The integer array parameter `candiesCount` must not be null.
- The 2D integer array parameter `queries` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `candiesCount` must have a length between 1 and 10^5.
- Each element in the integer array parameter `candiesCount` must be between 1 and 10^5.
- The 2D integer array parameter `queries` must have a length between 1 and 10^5.
- Each sub-array in the 2D integer array parameter `queries` must have a length of 3.
- The integer parameter `favoriteType` in each sub-array of the 2D integer array parameter `queries` must be between 0 and the length of the integer array parameter `candiesCount`.
- The integer parameter `favoriteDay` in each sub-array of the 2D integer array parameter `queries` must be between 0 and 10^9.
- The integer parameter `dailyCap` in each sub-array of the 2D integer array parameter `queries` must be between 1 and 10^9.
- The boolean array result `answer` must have a length equal to the length of the 2D integer array parameter `queries`.